Project Name: D'Clover

Land Area: 3.27 acres

Number of Blocks: 1 block

Number of Units: 593 units

Number of Floors: 46 levels

Freehold / Leasehold: Leasehold (95 years upon VP)

Completion Date: Not specified

Maintenance Fee + Sinking Fund: RM0.35 psf (including sinking fund)

Lifts per Floor: 5 + 1 lifts

Units per Floor: 13 units per floor (Level 9 and 24), 7 units per floor (Level 40 - 46)

Car Parks: Type A1, A2, A3, A4 - 2 single carparks, Type B1, B2, B3, B4 - 1 set tandem + 1 single carpark, Units with **** in sales chart come with 2 set tandem carpark

Tiers of Security: Multi-tier

Title: Commercial under HDA

Size: 1,210sf - 1,440sf

Price Range: From RM808,300 (gross)

Price per Square Feet: From RM668 psf (gross)

Sales Package:
Booking Fee: RM500

Loan buyer rebate package: 6% rebate + 2% rebate (if sign SPA within 14 days) upon SPA
Bumi Loan buyer rebate package: 6% rebate + 2% rebate (if sign SPA within 14 days) upon SPA + 2% rebate upon Stage 2B

Cash buyer rebate structure
5% rebate upon SPA
2% rebate upon Stage 2A
1% rebate upon VP

Additional rebate/discount (effective on 29/11/2022):
Lucky Draw Spin: Purchaser is entitled to a chance of lucky draw spin after payment of booking/deposit is made, with prizes ranging from RM7,999x2 , RM8,888x2 or RM9,999x2. Applicable only to D'Clover Level 1 until 13 only.

SPA Legal Fee: Absorbed by developer
SPA Disbursement Fee: Absorbed by developer
Loan Agreement Fee: Absorbed by developer
Loan Disbursement Fee: Absorbed by developer
Loan Stamp Duty: Absorbed by developer
MOT: Buyer has to pay

Cancellation Fee:
For projects without APDL or non HDA projects not yet proceeded for stamping:

With 2 genuine loan rejection letters: Only free gift to be charged (amount might vary based on project)
Without 2 loan rejection letters: Admin fees & legal fees + free gift (amount might vary based on project) will be charged
For projects with APDL or non HDA projects that can proceed for stamping:
For residential property (under HDA): 10% of SPA price below 50% payment, 20% of SPA price above 50% payment
For commercial property (under non HDA): 20% of SPA price below 50% payment, 30% of SPA price above 50% payment
Bare Unit: Only provided with air-conditioner in master bedroom and living hall, bathroom accessories

Company Name : MIGHTYPROP SDN. BHD. (1299882-V)
Name of Bank : RHB BANK BERHAD
HDA Account : 2-14129-0033540-0
Bank Address : LEVEL 1, TOWER TWO, RHB CENTRE, NO. 426, 
JALAN TUN RAZAK, 50400 KUALA LUMPUR.
Swift Code : RHBBMYKL

Panel Bank: Please refer to Exsim EF Approval Link in Atlas

Sales Gallery: EXSIM Sales Gallery (Empire City), Jalan Damansara Empire City, PJU 8, 47820 Petaling Jaya, Selangor, Operating Hours: 9am - 6pm everyday

IQI Incentive and Trips:  Yes

Commission Payout:
Loan buyer: Full claim within 5 working days once SPA signed, LA signed and 1st 10% payment made (100%)
Cash buyer: 
First claim once SPA signed, LA signed and 1st 10% payment made. Only 50% of the commission will be issued
Balance 50% commission claim will be issued within 3-8 months from the first commission received
*Note : This info is for your reference only; it may change accordingly without prior notice

Please be informed for Exsim comm payment 5 working days, it will be counted once ALL documents have received by Exsim.
5 working days wont be counted on the date of signing as many are doing online signing and it will take some time for the documents to courier back to Exsim.

Show unit types:
Type A2 - 1,210sf (Non Elderly, Non Balcony)
Type B3 - 1,440sf (Elderly, Balcony)

Commission Info:
If buyer entiled Referral fees, commission will be slashed by 13%
If buyer is a repeat buyer, REN comm 1% will be deducted
